<num value="10000">萬</num>徹<measure quantity="3" unit="people">
<num value="3">三</num>人</measure>而已<pc>，</pc>世勣<pc>、</pc>道宗不能大勝<pc>，</pc>亦不大敗<pc>，</pc>
<num value="10000">萬</num>徹非大勝則大敗<pc>。</pc>
